# Example environment file. Copy to `.Renviron` (which is git-ignored) and fill
# in real values. R reads `.Renviron` automatically on startup.
#
# CANDID uses ellmer for LLM access; set the key for the provider configured in
# config.yml. Default provider is Anthropic:
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Other ellmer-supported providers (uncomment the one you configure):
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_API_KEY=
